---
title: Donate — PauseAI UK
description: Support PauseAI UK — community-led action for safe and accountable AI.
canonical: /donate
ogTitle: Donate to PauseAI UK
ogDescription: Support community-led action for safe and accountable AI across the UK.
ogImage: /images/open-graph/open-graph-1200-630.jpg
ogImageWidth: 1200
ogImageHeight: 630
ogUrl: https://pauseai.uk/donate
twitterImage: /images/open-graph/open-graph-1600-840.jpg
noAnalytics: true
navPrefix: "/"
extraScripts:
  - src: /donate/donate.js
    defer: true
---
{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="donate-intro">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="donate-intro-grid">
        <div class="donate-intro-head">
          <p class="eyebrow">Support our work</p>
          <h1>Let's press pause on unsafe AI together</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="donate-intro-photo">
          <img
            src="/images/community.jpeg"
            alt="PauseAI UK volunteers at a community event"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="donate-intro-text">
          <p class="lede">
            PauseAI UK's work is done for and by citizens and communities
            across the country. We have already achieved a lot (see our
            <a class="inline-link" href="/track-record/">Track Record page</a>)
            with very limited resources, and we need to be doing a lot more
            and to scale fast.
          </p>
          <p class="lede">
            Your support is an important part of our capacity to act
            effectively. By donating, you empower every volunteer, our
            local groups and our small core team to run protests and other
            events, engage with decision makers and the press, support our
            community, produce outreach materials, build advocacy
            infrastructure and more. We're glad you're a part of this
            movement alongside us.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="donate-intro-form">
          <form class="donate-form" id="donate-form" novalidate>
            <div class="freq-toggle" role="radiogroup" aria-label="How you'd like to give">
              <button
                type="button"
                role="radio"
                aria-checked="true"
                data-freq="monthly"
                data-method="bacs_debit"
                class="freq-option is-active"
              >
                <span class="freq-name">Monthly</span>
                <span class="freq-method">Direct Debit</span>
              </button>
              <button
                type="button"
                role="radio"
                aria-checked="false"
                data-freq="oneoff"
                data-method="card"
                class="freq-option"
              >
                <span class="freq-name">One-off</span>
                <span class="freq-method">Card · Apple Pay · Google Pay</span>
              </button>
            </div>

            <fieldset class="amount-selector">
              <legend>Choose an amount</legend>
              <div class="amount-grid">
                <button type="button" class="amount-option" data-amount="3">£3</button>
                <button type="button" class="amount-option is-active" data-amount="5">£5</button>
                <button type="button" class="amount-option" data-amount="10">£10</button>
                <button type="button" class="amount-option" data-amount="25">£25</button>
                <button type="button" class="amount-option" data-amount="50">£50</button>
                <button type="button" class="amount-option" data-amount="100">£100</button>
                <button type="button" class="amount-option amount-other" data-amount="other">Other</button>
              </div>
              <div class="amount-custom" hidden>
                <label for="custom-amount">Enter amount</label>
                <div class="amount-input-wrap">
                  <span class="currency-prefix">£</span>
                  <input
                    type="number"
                    id="custom-amount"
                    name="custom-amount"
                    min="3"
                    step="1"
                    inputmode="numeric"
                    placeholder="3 or more"
                  />
                  <span class="amount-suffix" data-freq-suffix>per month</span>
                </div>
                <p class="amount-help">Minimum £3 per month.</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>

            <button
              type="submit"
              class="btn primary large donate-btn"
              id="donate-submit"
            >
              <span id="donate-cta-label">Donate £5 a month</span>
            </button>

            <p class="form-footnote">
              Payments are processed securely by
              <a href="https://stripe.com/en-gb/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Stripe</a>.
            </p>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section donate-bottom">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="donate-bottom-grid">

        <div id="other-ways" class="donate-bottom-col">
          <p class="eyebrow">Other ways to give</p>
          <h2>Major gifts &amp; bank transfer</h2>
          <p class="section-lede">
            If you're considering a larger gift, prefer to give by bank
            transfer, or represent a foundation, please get in touch.
          </p>
          <div class="other-ways-cards">
            <article class="feature-card">
              <h3>Bank transfer &amp; major donors</h3>
              <p>
                For UK bank transfers (Faster Payments / BACS) and gifts
                above £500, please email us so we can share account
                details directly.
              </p>
              <a
                class="inline-link"
                href="mailto:hello@pauseai.uk?subject=PauseAI%20UK%20donation%20enquiry"
              >hello@pauseai.uk →</a>
            </article>
            <article class="feature-card">
              <h3>US-based donors</h3>
              <p>
                We're working on enabling tax-deductible giving for US
                supporters. <em>Coming soon.</em>
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="transparency" class="donate-bottom-col">
          <p class="eyebrow">Trust &amp; transparency</p>
          <h2>Where your money goes</h2>
          <p class="section-lede">
            Your regular gift funds protests, organising, outreach materials,
            and the small staff team keeping this movement growing across
            the UK.
          </p>
          <p class="section-lede">
            Because our work meaningfully engages with policy, donations to
            us are not eligible for Gift Aid.
          </p>
          <p class="section-lede">
            Read our <a class="inline-link" href="/privacy">privacy policy</a>
            to learn how we handle your information.
          </p>
          <div class="registered-details">
            <p>
              <strong>Safe AI Alliance Ltd</strong> is the legal entity
              operating PauseAI UK. It is a private company limited by
              guarantee, registered in England and Wales (company number
              <strong>17137345</strong>), with registered office at 128
              City Road, London EC1V 2NX, United Kingdom.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}
